<h2>JournaLIPP (Zeitschriftenheft)</h2>
<h3>Gefährdete Sprachen - Endangered Languages</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='2436'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
